T1  - Dynamic Conditional Beta Is Alive and Well in the Cross Section of Daily Stock Returns
AU  - Bali, Turan G.
AU  - Engle, Robert F.
AU  - Tang, Yi
Y1  - 2016/09/09
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2017/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2536
